<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099877>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49–60. Specimens of Felderiola Naumann, 1971 and Monopetalotaxis Wallengren, 1859: 49–51. Felderiola karooensis new sp., Namibia, 15–16 km E Helmeringshausen, Lovedale guest farm, (49) ♂ holotype; (50–51) ♀ Paratype. 52– 54. Felderiola xanthogaster new sp., (52–53) ♀ holotype; (54) ♀, paratype. 55–60. Monopetalotaxis doleriformis (Walker, 1856), (55) ♂ holotype; (56) ♂ holotype of Aegeria taylori Druce, 1899; (57) ♂ holotype of Monopetalotaxis wahlbergi Wallengren, 1859; (58–59) ♂, Pretoria; (60) ♀, Johannesburg." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099877/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099885>
    dc:description "FIGURES 79–83. Living specimens and life-history of Felderiola karooensis new sp., Namibia, 15–16 km E Helmeringshausen, Lovedale guest farm: (79) ♂; (80) ♀; (81) larva; (82) root stock of the host plant with exit tube; (83) host plant Melolobium microphyllum (Fabaceae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099891>
    dc:description "FIGURES 99–106. Scanning electron microscope pictures of antennae: (99) Cicinnoscelis flavipes new sp., #f holotype; (100) Alonina rygchiiformis Walker, 1856; (101) Anaudia felderi Wallengren, 1863; (102) Austrosetia semirufa Felder & Felder, 1874; (103) Felderiola karooensis new sp.; (104) Monopetalotaxis doleriformis (Walker, 1856); (105) Hagnogyna bartschi (Freina, 2011); (106) Sesia bembeciformis (Hübner, 1803)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099903>
    dc:description "FIGURES 117–118. Male genitalia of Felderiola Naumann, 1971: (117) F. candescens (Felder & Felder, 1874); (118) F. karooensis new sp., paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10099913>
    dc:description "FIGURES 127–128. Female genitalia of Felderiola Naumann, 1971: (127) F. candescens (Felder & Felder, 1874); (128) F. karooensis new sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10099913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

